casebody.data:
REALTY APPRAISAL COMPANY, Plaintiff-Movant,
v.
CITY OF JERSEY CITY, a Municipal Corporation of the State of New Jersey, Defendant. M-633/634 September Term 2017
079689 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 26, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to file a motion for counsel fees and costs as within time (M-633) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion for counsel fees in the amount of $9,500.00 and costs of $44.30 is granted.
